of view and still bring

00:14:19.980 --> 00:14:23.870
in the higher semantics,
controlling the information content

00:14:23.870 --> 00:14:27.580
and the context of digital
audiovisual materials.

00:14:27.580 --> 00:14:31.420 position:56%
The recognition though that metadata
is no longer the sole responsibility

00:14:31.420 --> 00:14:34.530
of the cataloguer has
brought with it opportunities

00:14:34.530 --> 00:14:39.160
such as crowd sourcing, the
semantic web, automated tagging,

00:14:39.160 --> 00:14:42.730
and other mechanisms to
involve the public, collectors,

00:14:42.730 --> 00:14:44.260
and other interest groups.

00:14:44.260 --> 00:14:49.470 position:56%
The BBC and our very own organizing
knowledge committee are instrumental

00:14:49.470 --> 00:14:52.400
