these opportunities.

00:14:52.400 --> 00:14:54.200
The prospects being yielded

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:58.250
by the audiovisual digital
landscape are enormous and allow us

00:14:58.250 --> 00:15:01.590
to create central repositories
and stimulate collaboration

00:15:01.590 --> 00:15:04.930
and corporation within
