whether we like it or
not, between sort of--

00:31:47.100 --> 00:31:50.640
what I see is the maturation of
both technology and knowledge

00:31:50.640 --> 00:31:55.290
about technology, and the
fragility of the artifacts

00:31:55.290 --> 00:31:57.690
that we are increasingly
have to care for,

00:31:57.690 --> 00:32:00.700
especially the digitally born ones.

00:32:00.700 --> 00:32:04.570
And, you know, that's-- what you
