sort of metaphor for sometimes
how I feel as an archivist.

00:32:22.480 --> 00:32:24.940
It's my job, it's my
responsibility, it's my head,

00:32:24.940 --> 00:32:27.120
it's my, you know, stops with me.

00:32:27.120 --> 00:32:28.600
But sometimes, I have to just sort

00:32:28.600 --> 00:32:32.310
of watch it happen before
me at the same time.

00:32:32.310 --> 00:32:34.560
You know, this film,
Sunset Boulevard,

